Amelie Oudea-Castera\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Acting against the Games is acting against France, it's acting against your own camp, your own country.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999818046491, \"rank\": 1.8138989104350116e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"your own camp\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"your own country\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are not the Games of a government, they are the Games of a nation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"a government\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been no official statements over who might be behind the attacks.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no official statements\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"the attacks\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris prosecutors said in a statement that they are investigating the matter.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.1378165348475905e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"s