rg/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.1378165348475905e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its services\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"several trains\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It said high-speed trains going to and from Paris will be diverted, extending the journey time by around an hour and a half.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2242, \"end\": 2247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.1378165348475905e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high-speed trains\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"the journey time\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"around an hour\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Gare du Nord, Paris's Eurostar train station, a long line of people waited to reschedule their trips.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.1378165348475905e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2348, \"end\": 2356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999994116430483, \"rank\": 5.883573500333993e-07, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gare du Nord\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"a long line\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"their trips\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nabeel, a 24-year-old trainee analyst who lives and works in London but had been visiting his family in the Paris region, said he was able to switch to a slightly later train with no problem.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999994498991022, \"rank\": 5.041333571200355e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2537, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.1378165348475905e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nabeel\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"a 24-year-old trainee analyst\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"no problem\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he was told his trip would take longer than usual.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his trip\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In hindsight, I should have chosen another day,\\\" he said, declining to provide his full name for privacy reasons.\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hindsight\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"his full name\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"privacy reasons\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, chaos reigned at the key Paris rail hub of Montparnasse, with public address announcements